page.title: 19School Nature Trail
page.content: BIRDS: Kestrel,Sparrow,Blackbird, Thrush, Robin,House Martin,Bluetit, Yellowhammer, Bullfinch,Swallow, Magpie,Pigeon,Starling,Crow,Rook, Wagtail. HEDGEPLANTS: Hawthorn, Bramble,Holly,Privet,Dog Rose,Ivy, Nettle,Thistle,Cow parsley,Dock,Oak, "Granny Boot". TREES: Beech, Sycamore, Cedar (Atlas),Plum,Cherry, Oak, Fir,Elder. FLOWERS: Purple & White Alyssum,Tagetes,Marigold, Geranium,Bluebell,Golden Baum,White& Puurple Violet, Primula,White Lysanthus,Golden Macurum,Pink Forget me not,Periwinkle,Limanthes(Poached Egg Plant),Blue Forget me not, Dandelion,Buttercup,Daisy,Daffodil, Tulip,Crocus,Snowdrop,Moss,Lichen, Grasses,Clover,Deadnettles,Wildmint. INSECTS: Froghopper,Grasshopper,Fly, Caterpillar,Ladybird,Ant,Spider,Bee, Wasp,Slug,Snail,Worm.
